features: Travel Tissues for the Traveler: These pocket-sized tissue packs are right-sized and can be stored easily in a backpack, pants or jacket pocket, handbag, briefcase or in the car for on-the-go nasal relief

Need a Tissue, Got a Tissue: Great for weddings, throw these mini tissue packs into wedding themed party favor bags to help your guests to wipe their happy tears on the big day; the floral design also works well for funerals and graduations

Made for Everyday Use: Made of quality natural pulp paper, each tissue is 3-ply to ensure that they will be soft. Whether you're fighting a cold, or wiping away tears after celebrating at a special event, these individual small tissue packs are made to be used as often as needed
How They Measure: Each cream-colored tissue measures approximately 21 x 21 inches unfolded and comes in a slim travel size plastic holder for easy storage
What's Included: You will receive a bulk quantity of 24 travel-sized tissue packs in an elegant floral theme (240 tissues total)
body.description: These versatile tissue wipes are designed to provide convenience and comfort, wherever you go and whenever you need them. Crafted with softness in mind, these tissues are gentle on your nose and face, making them ideal for wiping away sniffles or freshening up on the go. However, their usefulness extends beyond facial care, as they can also be used to clean your hands when soap and water are not readily available. Measuring a compact 4.2 x 2.15 x 0.7 inches folded and in their individual dispenser, these tissues are perfectly sized for use as wedding party favors or even bachelorette party favors. Each pack features a flap pocket design, allowing you to conveniently access the tissue pack while keeping them clean and protected when not in use. With these travel-size tissues, you can be prepared for any situation that calls for a quick wipe with a touch of style. Whether you're attending a wedding, traveling, or simply going about your day, this bulk pack of portable wipes is a must-have companion.
